\frame{% how to print
\frametitle{Intra-Industry Trade}
\begin{itemize}
\item With product differentiation: each country produces different types of cloth.
\item economies of scale makes large markets are desirable: the foreign country exports some cloth and the domestic country exports some cloth.
\end{itemize}}

\frame{% how to print
